



































散發代理程式安全性 | Microsoft Docs



















散發代理程式安全性Distribution Agent Security


2017-3-14
5 分鐘可讀完
參與者










 [散發代理程式安全性] 對話方塊，可以讓您指定散發代理程式執行用的 Windows 帳戶。The Distribution Agent Security dialog box allows you to specify the Windows account under which the Distribution Agent runs. 若為發送訂閱，散發代理程式會在散發者端執行；若為提取訂閱，則散發代理程式會在訂閱者端執行。The Distribution Agent runs at the Distributor for push subscriptions and at the Subscriber for pull subscriptions. 此  MicrosoftMicrosoft Windows 帳戶亦稱為 處理帳戶，因為代理程式處理序會以此帳戶執行。The  MicrosoftMicrosoft Windows account is also referred to as the process account, because the agent process runs under this account. 對話方塊中其他可用的選項會視您存取的方式而定：Additional options available in the dialog box depend on how you access it: 

如果是從新增訂閱精靈中存取對話方塊，它還可以讓您指定散發代理程式連接到訂閱者 (適用於發送訂閱) 或散發者 (適用於提取訂閱) 所用的內容。If the dialog box is accessed from the New Subscription Wizard, it also allows you to specify the context under which the Distribution Agent makes connections to the Subscriber (for push subscriptions) or the Distributor (for pull subscriptions). 此連接可以藉由模擬 Windows 帳戶，或是用您指定之  MicrosoftMicrosoft SQL ServerSQL Server 帳戶的內容來進行。The connection can be made by impersonating the Windows account or under the context of a  MicrosoftMicrosoft SQL ServerSQL Server account you specify. 

如果是從 [訂閱屬性] 對話方塊中存取對話方塊，請按一下[訂閱者連接]中的屬性按鈕 ( ... )，或該對話方塊的 [散發者連接] 資料列，即可指定散發代理程式進行連接所用的內容。If the dialog box is accessed from the Subscription Properties dialog box, specify the context under which the Distribution Agent makes connections by clicking the properties button (...) in the Subscriber Connection or Distributor Connection row of that dialog box. 如需存取 [訂閱屬性] 對話方塊的詳細資訊，請參閱檢視及修改發送訂閱屬性和如何：檢視及修改提取訂閱屬性。For more information about accessing the Subscription Properties dialog box, see View and Modify Push Subscription Properties and how to: View and Modify Pull Subscription Properties. 
所有帳戶都必須有效，並且每個帳戶皆有指定正確的密碼。All accounts must be valid, with the correct password specified for each account. 等到代理程式執行時，才會驗證帳戶與密碼。Accounts and passwords are not validated until an agent runs. 


選項Options
 Process AccountProcess Account 輸入散發代理程式執行用的 Windows 帳戶：Enter a Windows account under which the Distribution Agent runs: 

針對發送訂閱，帳戶必須：For push subscriptions, the account must: 

至少是散發資料庫中 db_owner 固定資料庫角色的成員。At minimum be a member of the db_owner fixed database role in the distribution database. 

是發行存取清單 (PAL) 的成員。Be a member of the publication access list (PAL). 

擁有快照集共用上的讀取權限。Have read permissions on the snapshot share. 

如果訂閱是針對非 SQL ServerSQL Server 訂閱者，訂閱者之 OLE DB 提供者的安裝目錄上，就要擁有讀取權限。Have read permissions on the install directory of the OLE DB provider for the Subscriber if the subscription is for a non- SQL ServerSQL Server Subscriber. 



針對提取訂閱，帳戶至少必須是訂閱資料庫中之 db_owner 固定資料庫角色的成員。For pull subscriptions, the account must at minimum be a member of the db_owner fixed database role in the subscription database. 
如果是在進行連接時模擬處理帳戶，則需要其他的權限。Additional permissions are required if the process account is impersonated when connections are made. 請參閱以下的＜ 連接到散發者 ＞和＜ 連接到訂閱者 ＞章節。See the Connect to the Distributor and Connect to the Subscriber sections below. 
無法為 的提取訂閱指定  MicrosoftMicrosoft SQL Server ExpressSQL Server Express, because the Distribution Agent does not run on instances of  SQL Server ExpressSQL Server Express.Process Account cannot be specified for pull subscriptions to  MicrosoftMicrosoft SQL Server ExpressSQL Server Express, because the Distribution Agent does not run on instances of  SQL Server ExpressSQL Server Express. 
[密碼] 與 [確認密碼]Password and Confirm Password輸入 Windows 帳戶的密碼。Enter the password for the Windows account. 
連接到散發者Connect to the Distributor對於發送訂閱，要連接到散發者時，一律都會以模擬 [處理帳戶] 文字方塊中所指定的帳戶來進行。For push subscriptions, connections to the Distributor are always made by impersonating the account specified in the Process account text box. 
對於提取訂閱，選取散發代理程式是否應模擬 [處理帳戶] 文字方塊中所指定的帳戶，還是要使用  SQL ServerSQL Server 帳戶，來連接到散發者。For pull subscriptions, select whether the Distribution Agent should make connections to the Distributor by impersonating the account specified in the Process account text box or by using a  SQL ServerSQL Server account. 如果您選取使用  SQL ServerSQL Server 帳戶，請輸入  SQL ServerSQL Server 登入和密碼。If you select to use a  SQL ServerSQL Server account, enter a  SQL ServerSQL Server login and password. 


註意 建議您選取模擬 Windows 帳戶，而不要使用  SQL ServerSQL Server 帳戶。It is recommended that you select to impersonate the Windows account rather than using a  SQL ServerSQL Server account. 

 用於連接的 Windows 帳戶或  SQL ServerSQL Server 帳戶必須：The Windows account or  SQL ServerSQL Server account used for the connection must: 

為 PAL 的成員。Be a member of the PAL. 

擁有快照集共用上的讀取權限。Have read permissions on the snapshot share. 
連接到訂閱者Connect to the Subscriber針對提取訂閱，一律會藉由模擬 [處理帳戶] 文字方塊中指定的帳戶連接到訂閱者。For pull subscriptions, connections to the Subscriber are always made by impersonating the account specified in the Process account text box. 
對於發送訂閱，  SQL ServerSQL Server 訂閱者與非 SQL ServerSQL Server 訂閱者的選項並不相同：For push subscriptions, the options are different for  SQL ServerSQL Server Subscribers and non- SQL ServerSQL Server Subscribers: 

對於  SQL ServerSQL Server 訂閱者：選取散發代理程式是否應模擬 [處理帳戶] 文字方塊中所指定的帳戶，還是要使用  SQL ServerSQL Server 帳戶，來連接到訂閱者。For  SQL ServerSQL Server Subscribers: select whether the Distribution Agent should make connections to the Subscriber by impersonating the account specified in the Process account text box or by using a  SQL ServerSQL Server account. 如果您選取使用  SQL ServerSQL Server 帳戶，請輸入  SQL ServerSQL Server 登入和密碼。If you select to use a  SQL ServerSQL Server account, enter a  SQL ServerSQL Server login and password. 
註意 建議您選取模擬 Windows 帳戶，而不要使用  SQL ServerSQL Server 帳戶。It is recommended that you select to impersonate the Windows account rather than using a  SQL ServerSQL Server account. 

 用於連接到訂閱者的 Windows 帳戶或  SQL ServerSQL Server 帳戶至少必須是訂閱資料庫中之 db_owner 固定資料庫角色的成員。The Windows account or  SQL ServerSQL Server account used for the connection to the Subscriber must at minimum be a member of the db_owner fixed database role in the subscription database. 

對於非 SQL ServerSQL Server 訂閱者，請指定當散發代理程式要連接到訂閱者時，應使用的訂閱者端之資料庫登入。For non- SQL ServerSQL Server Subscribers, specify the database login at the Subscriber that should be used when the Distribution Agent connects to the Subscriber. 此登入應擁有在訂閱資料庫中建立物件的權限。The login should have sufficient permissions to create objects in the subscription database. 如需設定非  SQL ServerSQL Server 訂閱者的詳細資訊，請參閱為非 SQL Server 訂閱者建立訂閱。For more information about configuring non- SQL ServerSQL Server Subscribers, see Create a Subscription for a Non-SQL Server Subscriber. 
其他連接選項Additional connection options僅限非 SQL ServerSQL Server 訂閱者。Non- SQL ServerSQL Server Subscribers only. 以連接字串的格式，為訂閱者指定任何連接選項 (Oracle 並不需要其他選項)。Specify any connection options for the Subscriber in the form of a connection string (Oracle does not require additional options). 每個選項應以分號分隔。Each option should be separated by a semi-colon. 以下為 IBM DB2 連接字串的範例 (分行符號僅為便於閱讀)：The following is an example of an IBM DB2 connection string (line breaks are for readability): 


Provider=DB2OLEDB;Initial Catalog=MY_SUBSCRIBER_DB;Network Transport Library=TCP;Host CCSID=1252;  
PC Code Page=1252;Network Address=MY_SUBSCRIBER;Network Port=50000;Package Collection=MY_PKGCOL;  
Default Schema=MY_SCHEMA;Process Binary as Character=False;Units of Work=RUW;DBMS Platform=DB2/NT;  
Persist Security Info=False;Connection Pooling=True;  
 字串中的大多數選項是您設定之 DB2 伺服器的專用選項，但 將二進位當作字元處理 選項，應一律設定為 [False] 。Most of the options in the string are specific to the DB2 server you are configuring, but the Process Binary as Character option should always be set to False. 需要為 初始目錄 選項指定值，以便識別訂閱資料庫。A value is required for the Initial Catalog option to identify the subscription database. 如需相關資訊，請參閱 IBM DB2 Subscribers。For more information, see IBM DB2 Subscribers. 
